data.description: Welcome to 102 Buena Vista Circle South, a home nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac in the Lake Forest neighborhood.  Off the front porch and stepping through the front door reveals a warm and inviting foyer with hardwood floors, and natural light comes in through the large windows, illuminating the spacious living areas.  The living room comes with a cozy fireplace and a mantelpiece for decorating, perfect for gathering on cold evenings. The kitchen features modern appliances with classic cabinetry and granite countertops. A breakfast nook bathed in sunlight offers a delightful spot to enjoy morning coffee while overlooking the backyard.  Upstairs leads to the bedrooms and full baths, each with plenty of room. The master suite has a  spacious en suite bathroom and ample closet space. Other bedrooms offer versatility and charm, ideal for accommodating family or guests.  Outside, the backyard provides plenty of privacy. A patio, ideal for entertaining, overlooks your lawn. Tall trees provide shade and a sense of seclusion, making it an ideal spot for outdoor gatherings or relaxation.
